{"tid":2157961,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"睇彼女お借りします，喺中同谷畀人串雞蟲！點反擊班死MK....18+","createTime":"2020-08-15T11:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T12:54:32.000Z","uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2d21ddd2dc4777b6e51974869c88ff907a1ef0a6","tid":2157961,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Up56ppa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUp56ppa.jpg&h=1a1c4b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中學畢業一年就來year 2，有加中同谷平時好少出聲...<br />\n<br />\n呢排果青出第三季，班中同好似都有睇...有時討論下咁<br />\n<br />\n見佢地會講狗派同貓派...爭得好犀利...<br />\n<br />\n我諗住做和事佬叫佢地睇彼女お借りします，話入面啲囡囡仲好性格，劇情好睇...<br />\n<br />\n點知班MK冇啦啦話咩ptgf姐係做雞...咩賣淫...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後同佢地嘈左成日...係咁解釋做ptgf還ptgf唔係做雞，冇出賣肉體！<br />\n<br />\n依加佢地幫我改左個花名叫雞蟲...話叫開ptgf先鍾意睇依啲...搞到我好嬲！！<br />\n<br />\n屌兩樣嘢根本唔同，究竟有幾難明！<br />\n<br />\n各位動物台台友覺得點反擊佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1373906b28c9cb3ce4937ec32e8c4ce456adf6","tid":2157961,"uid":56550,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"吞槍自殺顯示自己清白"},{"pid":"6cdbd856b862001bc7334a3898f3712eeef67317","tid":2157961,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c1373906b28c9cb3ce4937ec32e8c4ce456adf6","tid":2157961,"uid":56550,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"吞槍自殺顯示自己清白"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"想佢地有報應..."},{"pid":"1466db45b6d4256c94873e223f9e70a2dfb97b33","tid":2157961,"uid":56550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"拎槍指住佢地<br />\n叫佢地唔好再話你叫開ptgf"},{"pid":"d0f71da47cf50cad79c05f52e405ef94095ca224","tid":2157961,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cdbd856b862001bc7334a3898f3712eeef67317","tid":2157961,"uid":105678,"like"